column16: Mark DeRosa pops out to shortstop Jimmy Rollins.
Rick Ankiel singles on a line drive to left fielder John Mayberry.    Matt Holliday to 3rd.
Brendan Ryan lines out to third baseman Pedro Feliz.
Albert Pujols grounds out, shortstop Jimmy Rollins to first baseman Ryan Howard.    Julio Lugo scores.
Julio Lugo triples (3) on a fly ball to center fielder Shane Victorino.
Skip Schumaker grounds out to first baseman Ryan Howard.
Joe Thurston called out on strikes.  Rick Ankiel steals (2) 3rd base.  Jason LaRue steals (1) 2nd base.
Mark DeRosa flies out to left fielder John Mayberry.
Rick Ankiel doubles (18) on a line drive to right fielder Jayson Werth.
